@baseUrl = http://localhost:3097
@tenantId = f63421a5-f5b2-11f0-937d-1a220d8ac2c9

### Get audit change history for an estate_estate entity record
GET {{baseUrl}}/audit/estate_estate/1
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}
Accept: application/json

### Get audit change history for an estate_unit entity record
GET {{baseUrl}}/audit/estate_unit/42
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}
Accept: application/json

### Get audit change history for an estate_person entity record
GET {{baseUrl}}/audit/estate_person/7
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}
Accept: application/json

### Get audit change history for an entity with no history (returns empty array)
GET {{baseUrl}}/audit/estate_vehicle/999
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}
Accept: application/json
